For the past 10 years I've been creating music videos for artists so it's insane to have some of my closest friends make mine.  Huge thank you to Vanseco, Agustin Seco & the Neon Boy who put this entire music video together.  They've been supporting my music since day 1 and are so talented!  

Shout out to all the dancers in this, follow them below!  You guys are all so inspiring and have such amazing energy, THANK YOU for being part of this.  Special thx to Gilly who I just realized has now been in all 3 music videos I've released, my bro!!

And thank you to everyone who has been supporting my music and sharing videos like this.  It's not about music OR dance, it's about bringing the communities together and uplifting both.  This is just the beginning!

