DanceCon is a reality show where the challenge is to put together workshops, auditions & a video shoot in a random city in only 2 days!!  

Dancers that get chosen at the audition immediately go into rehearsals for the video with less than 24 hours to learn the routine and film a dance concept video with Matt and his LA production team.  

